rc=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41f382da914b195c33c99ecebaed35392fe25f1","tid":1982424,"uid":214368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:12:11.000Z","msg":"推上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5141452d6f0ed71f041d589e95e2626312893d","tid":1982424,"uid":214368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f867a12f1717fe82a2182e7b3aa56232a4b403f","tid":1982424,"uid":214368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1491f87ed20a4d9ac72db5bd8feb5d1ca105915","tid":1982424,"uid":214368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKeBQN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKeBQN5.jpg&h=33265099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2020 DSE 考生備忘 &mdash; 考前一個禮拜篇】<br />\n有啲嘢想提下就嚟應考嘅你🔥<br />\n<br />\n1｜每日早睡早起<br />\n通常8點半就開考，確保當刻會立即進入到狀態嘅話，就千祈唔好夜瞓，比自己習慣大概7點起身。<br />\n<br />\n2｜戒食熱氣食物<br />\n開始戒食熱氣、煎炸、生冷食物，飲凍嘢都最好唔好喇。<br />\n<br />\n3｜養成早餐習慣<br />\n考試之前最好食早餐，無食開早餐嘅要比自己身體習慣下。<br />\n<br />\n4｜熟悉考場位置<br />\n有時間嘅最好預先去一次考場，確保知道位置之餘，仲可以方便預要幾耐去到。<br />\n<br />\n5｜揀選合適文具<br />\n揀好平時覺得好寫嘅筆同用得舒服嘅文具，唔建議突然轉用冇用開嘅，避免用唔慣。<br />\n<br />\n6｜準備雞精筆記<br />\n準備好入考場之前會睇嘅last minute notes，一定要係精簡嘅，因為考之前冇時間俾你將大量筆記塞入腦。<br />\n<br />\n遲啲會出埋「應考當日篇」！<br />\n或者去我哋ig睇啦🤟🏻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B_HhUXZlpmS/?igshid=13ig6lw7hcsv8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_HhUXZlpmS%2F%3Figshid%3D13ig6lw7hcsv8&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=078ef19b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB_HhUXZlpmS%2F%3Figshid%3D13ig6lw7hcsv8&h=f4ba9d27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B_HhUXZlpmS/?igshid=13ig6lw7hcsv8</a>"},{"pid":"a2e8698d9ca154a29b76b821d76fc94df089eee0","tid":1982424,"uid":214368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"大家DSE要加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3ded94e8cee98cfe18fa087c516715ea61f490","tid":1982424,"uid":214368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:53:40.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0cef04756f266fdccbab0af44af96373dfebdd","tid":1982424,"uid":214368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4c549ec7ab1826d6a16dfcde2bd1924739edf1","tid":1982424,"uid":86127,"lik